name: DAYBREAK HAZE
description: Only essential sensations. Only essential colors remain after a night under the Greek sky. The memory of all the stars is overwhelming. We wake up on top of each other and I’m numb. There is a pornstar with a drone right next to us. We grab a coffee and smoke some weed. Apparently, there are scorpions on the beach at night. What you don’t know can make up for peculiar choices
